article.description: — Michael Ertel tied his season high with 21 points as UAB topped North Texas 65-51 on Friday night.
article.headline: Ertel scores 21 to carry UAB over North Texas 65-51
article.linkText: Ertel scores 21 to carry UAB over North Texas 65-51
article.story: DENTON, Texas -- — Michael Ertel tied his season high with 21 points as UAB topped North Texas 65-51 on Friday night. Tavin Lovan had 12 points for UAB (20-6, 12-5 Conference USA). Trey Jemison added 11 points. Kassim Nicholson had 10 points and nine rebounds. Javion Hamlet had 16 points for the Mean Green (13-8, 9-4). Thomas Bell added 12 points and eight rebounds. Zachary Simmons had 10 points and nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
